_

23:03.387 --> 23:04.586
Mm?

23:04.622 --> 23:05.954
[Chuckles]

23:05.990 --> 23:07.990
_

23:08.025 --> 23:10.359
[Laughs]

23:10.394 --> 23:12.461
- [Bell clinks]
- [Sighs]

23:12.496 --> 23:13.511
_

23:14.591 --> 23:18.971
_

23:19.036 --> 23:20.969
Mm-hmm.

23:21.005 --> 23:22.638
_

