38:26.335 --> 38:27.667
[Gunshot]

38:27.703 --> 38:30.804
[Engine rumbling]

38:57.766 --> 39:02.068
[Machinery whirring]

39:02.104 --> 39:05.372
[Indistinct conversations]

39:05.407 --> 39:08.308
-You're good.
-Hold up.

39:08.343 --> 39:10.844
[Indistinct conversations]

39:10.879 --> 39:12.479
Man: Okay, I can do that.

39:12.514 --> 39:16.917
[Radio chatter]

39:16.952 --> 39:19.319
[Indistinct conversations]

39:30.966 --> 39:32.232
[Machinery whirring]

39:34.703 --> 39:40.407
[Indistinct conversations]

39:44.780 --> 39:47.948
[Dog sniffing]

39:47.983 --> 39:50.250
[Indistinct conversations]

39:57.893 --> 40:01.061
[Whines softly]

40:01.096 --> 40:03.864
Looks like we got a hit.

40:03.899 --> 40:06.099
[Tires screech]

40:06.134 --> 40:07.234
[Siren wailing]

40:07.269 --> 40:09.970
[Sirens wailing]

40:10.005 --> 40:11.238
[Brakes squeal]

40:11.273 --> 40:12.739
Officer: Get down on your knees!

40:16.111 --> 40:19.479
[Grunts]

40:19.514 --> 40:20.914
[Handcuffs clicking]

40:20.949 --> 40:23.116
[Indistinct conversations]

40:23.151 --> 40:27.320
[Insects chirping]

40:30.125 --> 40:34.494
[Sighs]

41:00.188 --> 41:02.355
[Siren wails in distance]

41:02.391 --> 41:04.958
[Chirping continues]

41:12.834 --> 41:14.367
[Sighs]

41:14.403 --> 41:16.836
[Spits] Jesus. How old is this?

41:16.872 --> 41:19.105
I found it in the glove box.

41:19.141 --> 41:20.840
- [Chuckles]
- Best guess?

41:20.876 --> 41:23.443
From back when all the doors matched.

41:23.478 --> 41:25.111
- [Chuckles]
- [Sniffles]

41:25.147 --> 41:26.780
[Clears throat]

41:26.815 --> 41:30.750
I got a deal offer from the ADA today.

41:32.154 --> 41:33.720
And?

41:33.755 --> 41:35.689
It's not what I expected.

41:35.724 --> 41:37.724
Bad not what you expected?

41:37.759 --> 41:40.727
[Sighs] It's just that...

41:40.762 --> 41:43.863
It's different.

41:43.899 --> 41:47.133
She's offering me Pre-Prosecution Diversion.

41:47.169 --> 41:48.902
Seriously?

41:48.937 --> 41:51.338
A PPD?

41:51.373 --> 41:52.739
[Chuckles]

41:52.774 --> 41:55.542
That's great, Jimmy.

41:55.577 --> 41:56.910
[Scoffs]

41:56.945 --> 41:58.912
Best I could hope for, right?

41:58.947 --> 42:00.180
Right.

42:00.215 --> 42:02.482
What does she want you to confess to?

42:02.517 --> 42:04.884
All of it. The felony B and E.

42:04.920 --> 42:08.054
Uh, misdemeanor petty assault
and property damage.

42:08.090 --> 42:11.324
I never touched him,
but they got assault in there.

42:11.360 --> 42:12.926
Well, could be worse.

42:12.961 --> 42:14.928
As long as they never activate it,

42:14.963 --> 42:16.763
it doesn't matter, right?

42:16.798 --> 42:20.367
You gonna be able to keep your
nose clean for a whole year?

42:20.402 --> 42:23.036
Keep "Viktor" with a "k" on lockdown?

42:23.071 --> 42:25.171
It's not a problem, Giselle.

42:25.207 --> 42:27.941
And if I don't, it's instant jail, right?

42:27.976 --> 42:29.743
[Exhales deeply]

42:29.778 --> 42:31.177
Lucky break.

42:31.213 --> 42:33.947
She must not want the hassle of a trial.

42:33.982 --> 42:37.517
[Clicks tongue] Guess so.

42:37.552 --> 42:39.386
Jimmy...

42:39.421 --> 42:40.954
this is good news.

42:40.989 --> 42:43.590
And Chuck is gonna be pissed.

42:43.625 --> 42:45.592
It's a big check in the "pro" column.

42:45.627 --> 42:49.229
Actually, the PPD was Chuck's idea.

42:50.265 --> 42:52.065
Shit.

42:52.100 --> 42:53.933
Yeah.

42:55.237 --> 42:57.937
[Breathes deeply] What's his game?

42:57.973 --> 43:01.808
One condition of the PPD
is that my written confession

43:01.843 --> 43:05.412
is immediately submitted to
the New Mexico Bar Association.

43:05.447 --> 43:07.480
Your written <i>felony</i> confession.

43:07.516 --> 43:09.616
Yeah. I thought he wanted me in jail.

43:09.651 --> 43:12.218
He just wants my law license.

43:12.254 --> 43:13.753
[Sighs]

43:14.823 --> 43:16.823
What are you gonna do?

43:16.858 --> 43:18.625
Well...

43:18.660 --> 43:21.828
I knew the bar was gonna be an issue, right?

43:21.863 --> 43:23.630
So I figured I'd plea the charges down

43:23.665 --> 43:25.432
to a couple misdemeanors, get a censure,

43:25.467 --> 43:28.568
and maybe a little suspension, but...

43:28.603 --> 43:30.837
a confession to a felony?

43:30.872 --> 43:32.739
Grounds for disbarment.

43:32.774 --> 43:35.442
Yeah. And if I take it to trial and I lose,

43:35.477 --> 43:38.144
I face the bar anyways
and jail time, most likely.

43:38.180 --> 43:39.412
[Sighs]

43:39.448 --> 43:41.681
He's got me boxed in.

43:44.286 --> 43:46.152
You can fight this.

43:46.188 --> 43:48.621
The disciplinary board listens
to extenuating circumstances.

43:48.657 --> 43:51.124
No, Chuck knows everybody at the bar.

